{"tid":1947022,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Trump: 習近平做得很好. 中國將向美國提供大量數據.","createTime":"2020-03-28T04:12:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-28T05:14:03.000Z","uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"7260f787e3dd9ea7546fbcb06ff03bb757d772ba","tid":1947022,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T04:12:00.000Z","msg":"Donald Trump稱讚中國與英國, 對德國卻輕輕帶過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.whitehouse.gov/briefings-statements/remarks-president-trump-signing-h-r-748-cares-act/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whitehouse.gov%2Fbriefings-statements%2Fremarks-president-trump-signing-h-r-748-cares-act%2F&d=g1YLBr7c5t2fgTVFseaOq5Urr29XULmfQ5XcAAvzh4c%3D&h=96ca0925\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.whitehouse.gov/briefings-statements/remarks-president-trump-signing-h-r-748-cares-act/</a><br />\n<br />\n<em>I said hello today &mdash; I called him &mdash; a wonderful guy, Boris Johnson.  As you know, he tested positive.  And before he even said hello, he said, &ldquo;We need ventilators.&rdquo;  I said, &ldquo;Wow.  That&rsquo;s a big statement.&rdquo;  And hopefully, he&rsquo;s going to be in good shape.<br />\n<br />\nI just spoke to Angela Merkel, and she&rsquo;s quarantined also.  She is right now, for a period of two weeks, being forced to stay in her house.  So this is just an incredible situation.<br />\n<br />\nLast night, I spoke to President Xi.  We talked about the experience that they had in China and all of the things that have taken place.  And we learned a lot.  <strong>They&rsquo;ve had a very tough experience, and they&rsquo;re doing well and he&rsquo;s doing well.  President Xi is doing very well.  But we learned a lot and we have great communication together.</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>We&rsquo;re going to be sent great data from China</strong> &mdash; things that happened that they see that &mdash; you know, they&rsquo;ve had a &mdash; they&rsquo;ve had an early experience, and we&rsquo;re getting all of that information.  Much of it has already been sent.  It was sent yesterday and sent to our scientists to study.  So we&rsquo;ll have more on that also.  We&rsquo;ll be discussing that at 5:30.</em>"},{"pid":"044320acb7d0b66649d06fbc8d25da570ae4dcbf","tid":1947022,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T04:12:09.000Z","msg":"德國政權, 美國Trump 民望大升<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1946230/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1946230/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"8b15a7298c4a26e3e672ebd968ff6c591b8c71c9","tid":1947022,"uid":223741,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T04:12:40.000Z","msg":"支那吹水大會正式開始"},{"pid":"6a6be1852e653baf34a659e530b5858e7a812a44","tid":1947022,"uid":297997,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T04:13:13.000Z","msg":"2000千萬人死左既數據"},{"pid":"447f2b41dce264decd991c6f4719f5205d22e98c","tid":1947022,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T04:13:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13b258f332983f27656dfe7533123ecf769f8142","tid":1947022,"uid":225798,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T04:13:59.000Z","msg":"反話？"},{"pid":"cbe54b52a5dcb6b58740a1cae3771560f3e23778","tid":1947022,"uid":297997,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"13b258f332983f27656dfe7533123ecf769f8142","tid":1947022,"uid":225798,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T04:13:59.000Z","msg":"反話？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T04:14:38.000Z","msg":"he feels he did it well"},{"pid":"ed63f957341694a9e61d4916043bc03b2696c556","tid":1947022,"uid":210031,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T04:16:24.000Z","msg":"唔駛理佢講乜，Trump 不嬲彈出彈入<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" 